targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT t, groupArray((concat('Elevation ', sat), elevation)) AS groupArr FROM ( SELECT (intDiv(time, (1)) * (1)) AS t, sat, avg(elevation) elevation FROM computed.satxyz2
WHERE "d" >= toDate(1679301197) AND "d" <= toDate(1679301497) AND time >= toUInt64(1679301197 * 1000) AND time <= toUInt64(1679301497 * 1000) AND
    sat = 'GPS6' GROUP BY t, sat ORDER BY t, sat) GROUP BY t ORDER BY t

targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
$columns(
    'C/No %sat %freq',
    avg(cno) cno)
FROM $table
WHERE
    sat = '$satgraph'
    AND freq IN ($freq)
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT t, groupArray((concat('C/No ', sat, ' ', freq), cno)) AS groupArr FROM ( SELECT (intDiv(time, (1)) * (1)) AS t, sat, freq, avg(cno) cno FROM computed.range
WHERE "d" >= toDate(1679301197) AND "d" <= toDate(1679301497) AND time >= toUInt64(1679301197 * 1000) AND time <= toUInt64(1679301497 * 1000) AND
    sat = 'GPS6'
    AND freq IN ('L1CA') GROUP BY t, sat, freq ORDER BY t, sat, freq) GROUP BY t ORDER BY t

targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
SELECT
    t,
    groupArray((concat('TEC ', sat, ' ', sigcomb), nt)) AS groupArr
FROM
(
    SELECT
        (intDiv(time, 1000) * 1000) as t,
        sat,
        sigcomb,
        avg(nt) nt
    FROM computed.NT final

    WHERE
        $timeFilterMs
        AND sat = '$satgraph'
        and sigcomb in ($sigcomb)
    GROUP BY
        t,
        sat,
        sigcomb
    ORDER BY
        t,
        sat,
        sigcomb
)
GROUP BY t

ORDER BY t
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT
    t,
    groupArray((concat('TEC ', sat, ' ', sigcomb), nt)) AS groupArr
FROM
(
    SELECT
        (intDiv(time, 1000) * 1000) as t,
        sat,
        sigcomb,
        avg(nt) nt
    FROM computed.NT final

    WHERE
        "d" >= toDate(1679301321) AND "d" <= toDate(1679301621) AND time >= toUInt64(1679301321780/1000 * 1000) AND time <= toUInt64(1679301621780/1000 * 1000)
        AND sat = 'GPS6'
        and sigcomb in ('L1CA+L2P_codeless','L1CA+L2C','L1CA+L5Q')
    GROUP BY
        t,
        sat,
        sigcomb
    ORDER BY
        t,
        sat,
        sigcomb
)
GROUP BY t

ORDER BY t

    secondaryfreq IN ('L2C')

targets.query:
$columns(
    'ПИТ sat=%sat',
    any(ionpoint) g)
FROM $table
WHERE sat IN ($satvis)
targets.rawQuery: SELECT t, groupArray((concat('ПИТ sat=', sat), g)) as groupArr FROM ( SELECT intDiv(time, 1000) * 1000 as t, sat, any(ionpoint) g FROM computed.satxyz2 WHERE d >= toDate(1656762638574/1000) AND time >= 1656762638574 AND  sat IN ('GLONASS1') GROUP BY t, sat  ORDER BY t, sat) GROUP BY t ORDER BY t

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  sat,
  (time / 1000) * 1000               AS time,
  anyLast(ionpointStr)               AS ionpoint,
  anyLast(s4.s4)                     AS s4,
  anyLast(elevation)                 AS elevation,

  (geohashDecode(ionpoint) AS tpl).1 AS latitude,
  tpl.2                              AS longitude
FROM
  computed."satxyz2" AS xyz
INNER JOIN (
  SELECT
    time,
    sat,
    s4
  FROM
    computed.s4
  WHERE
    time BETWEEN ($__to - 1000) AND $__to) AS s4
ON
  s4.sat == xyz.sat
  AND s4.time == xyz.time
WHERE
  xyz.time BETWEEN ($__to - 1000) AND $__to
GROUP BY
  sat,
  time
ORDER BY
  time
